    "body": "@tuyennhv As I summarized in https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/1771\r\nIn terms of speeding up signature verification, it has 3 steps\r\n- Change herumi for BLST, x10 speed increase :heavy_check_mark: \r\n- Use batch verification x2 speed increase :hourglass: \r\n- Multi-thread x2-x8 speed increase :question: \r\n\r\nSo the most impactful speed increase is already delivered. That's why I think it's a good time to benchmark how good or bad are we right now.",
